: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ff8be6291a57ac7e9a6e6a1de6f28fb711c4229","tid":1540860,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab80d96ea4628ec17664a09dcad346982b6b828f","tid":1540860,"uid":261430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:51:10.000Z","msg":"動議咋<br />\n笑咩?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:06:06.000Z","msg":"挫士氣，好見駛"},{"pid":"5cbecb12167c562dc6252a1a6cca647ccb63aa98","tid":1540860,"uid":23160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:06:45.000Z","msg":"笑?你贏左?"},{"pid":"a8ad8c925b2a191058ee5611b2a738ec5206c503","tid":1540860,"uid":204625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e38ec61bd0abcafc815b8fb7bd2fa75b546d1a","tid":1540860,"uid":204625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:09:39.000Z","msg":"721 831"},{"pid":"cbe60b3da71602d35ec4a58220bd928adc92344c","tid":1540860,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cbecb12167c562dc6252a1a6cca647ccb63aa98","tid":1540860,"uid":23160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:06:45.000Z","msg":"笑?你贏左?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:14:02.000Z","ms